Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.63,0:04:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈在干什么\NWhat the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.90,0:04:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,试着找你背着我藏起来的东西\NTrying to find what you've been hiding from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.42,0:04:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,比如我妈妈的日记\NLike my mom's journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我没有  小詹姆斯\NI don't have it, Junior.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.62,0:04:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,有人把它偷走了\NSomeone stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,莱尔偷的\NThat was Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.01,0:04:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,莱尔在监狱里\NLyle's in jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,直到我偷偷把他放了出来\NHe was until I snuck him out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,他告诉我说我妈妈的日记里有预言\NHe told me my mom's journal had predictions in it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,比如谁会杀了安琪\Nlike who was gonna kill Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,你有什么发现\NWhat'd you find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.13,0:04:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没查到  他袭击了我\NI didn't get that far. He attacked me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.53,0:04:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,然后带着日记跑了\Nand he ran off with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.26,0:04:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,他不想让我看到里面的内容\NHe didn't want me to see what was in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.23,0:04:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,所以一定是他杀了安琪  对吗\NSo he must have killed Angie, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,他总是有点疯癫\NHe always has been a little nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,日记中的好多页没了\NPages missing from the journal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得如果我找到了\NI thought if I'd find it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.23,0:04:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就能知道他去了哪里\NI'd be able to figure out where he's going
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,或者他接下来要做什么\Nor what he's gonna do next,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.76,0:04:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,或者他要逃到哪里\Nor where he's run off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.29,0:04:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你什么也找不到\NYou won't find anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果莱尔伤害到别人  就是我的错\NIf Lyle hurts somebody else, it's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.62,0:04:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那么我们一起阻止他\NSo we'll stop him together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.22,0:05:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我不该相信他  不管我妈妈说什么\NI should have never trusted him, no matter what my mom said.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈让你相信莱尔吗\NYour mother told you to trust Lyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.53,0:05:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,在她死前\NBefore she died?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.30,0:05:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,两天前  她给我发了一封电邮\NTwo days ago, she sent me an e-mail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,她还活着\NShe's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,她在外面的某处\NShe's out there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.62,0:05:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我还在想你们俩何时会出现\NI was wondering when you two would show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在找卡罗琳和孩子们\NYeah, we're just looking for Carolyn and the kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.07,0:05:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在后面\NIn the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以给你们拿点麦片  土司和茶\NI can bring you cereal, toast and tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.94,0:05:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,食物是哪来的\NWhere'd you get all the food?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,地下室的秘密储粮\NSecret store in the basement.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.77,0:05:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,安琪告诉我的  愿她安息\NAngie told me about it, God rest her soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.87,0:05:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都在等着开镇民大会  茱莉亚\NOh, and we're all waiting for the town meeting, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她在这里用餐  我就离开\NIf she's eating here, I ain't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,镇里来去自由\NHey, it's a free town.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.00,0:05:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,大个儿吉姆入狱后就不自由了\NNot since Big Jim went to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.57,0:05:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我没听错吧  格雷格\NI hear you right, Greg?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.92,0:05:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你要跟那个试图用病毒\NYou throwing your lot in with the guy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,杀死所有人的家伙站在一边吗\Nwho tried to murder everyone with that virus of his?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.84,0:05:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆才没有用什么病毒\NJim wasn't caught with no virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,这是陷害\NIt was a set-up, all right,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.19,0:05:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,-这样她就能掌权  让他受审  -别碰我\N- so she can take over and put him on trial. - Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,够了\NWhoa, whoa, whoa! That's enough. Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.07,0:06:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,退后\Njust back off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.74,0:06:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你的审判\NThis trial of yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.37,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,最好做出正确的裁决\NIt better reach the right verdict.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.24,0:06:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到莱尔了吗\NDid you find Lyle?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,还没有\NNot yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,小詹姆斯和我整夜都在镇里找他\NJunior and I spent all night combing the town for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.98,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,但一无所获\Nbut no sign of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该出去找他\NI should be out there looking for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是个火药桶\NThis place is a powder keg.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不  我要你们三个今天低调行事\NNo, I want the three of you to lie low today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,审判必须快点开始\NThis trial has to happen soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.08,0:06:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我打算在镇民大会上\NI'm planning on reading the charges
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.38,0:06:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,宣读吉姆和丽贝卡的罪名\Nagainst Jim and Rebecca at the town meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:30.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他们还需要代理律师\NThey'll need representation, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,希望你能帮忙\NWhich is where you come in, I hope?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.27,0:06:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,老妈当大个儿吉姆的律师\NMom as Big Jim's lawyer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.09,0:06:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,他绝对要被判有罪了\NHe's so totally guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.33,0:06:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,所有人都应得到公正的审判\NEveryone deserves a fair trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.61,0:06:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜我应该去\NWell, I guess I'll go,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,陪我的新客户去市政厅了\Nuh, escort my new clients to the town hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,那里见  茱莉亚\NI'll see you there, Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.89,0:06:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢  卡罗琳\NThank you, Carolyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉了茱莉亚\NI filled Julia in
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.17,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们发现的关于梅兰妮的所有事\Non everything that we found out about Melanie,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但是只有茱莉亚知道\Nbut only Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉昨天没有和你在一起  梅兰妮\NI'm really sorry that I wasn't there with you yesterday, Melanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.25,0:06:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在知道自己是谁了\NI know who I am now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.18,0:07:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,但我为什么会回来\Nbut why am I back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  但一定有原因\NI don't know, but there is a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证我会查出来\NI promise I'll find out what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆会去市政厅\NSam will be at the town hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.38,0:07:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,芭比和我会跟他谈谈\NBarbie and I will talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.58,0:07:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗  但是他说得对\NAll right, but he's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.95,0:07:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,你们留下  好吗\NYou kids stay. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们先问出答案\NLet us get some answers first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.74,0:07:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚发现我死了\NI just found out I died.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.51,0:07:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能坐在这里袖手旁观\NI can't just sit around and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧  我知道该去哪里\NCome on, I know where to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,有人吗\NAnybody out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,够了  吉姆  我头疼\NOkay, enough, Jim. I've got a headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.22,0:07:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,你头疼是吗\NOh, you got a headache, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我快要在这里饿死了\NI'm just about starving in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  只过了一晚\NCome on. It's only been one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.10,0:07:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚保证会有审判\NJulia promised a trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,她会来找我们的\NShe'll come for us, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,对  她当然会来\NYeah, she'll come for us, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.56,0:07:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,然后呢\NThen what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她要绞死我们吗\NShe gonna hang us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我们只是不想让大家饿死\NWe were just trying to keep everyone from starving to death.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.09,0:07:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,现在所有人都以为我是连环杀手\NNow everyone thinks I'm some sort of serial killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是你的错\Nand it's all your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.83,0:07:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你说服我该进行你的计划\NYou convinced me that your plan's the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.23,0:07:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,然后你骗了我  让我没做成\NAnd then you... then you tricked me into not being able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.56,0:07:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我告诉你了\NI told you,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,病毒比我想象的更强大\Nthe virus was stronger than I thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果情况改变  你也必须改变思维\NIf the evidence changes, your thinking has to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.59,0:08:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这叫科学\NIt's called science.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我不在乎你怎么叫\NI don't care what you call it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,现在人人都想让我们见血\NNow everybody's out there for our blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.32,0:08:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢大家今天前来\NThanks, everyone, for joining me today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.53,0:08:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道这周很不好过\NI know it's been a rough week,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.52,0:08:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得是时候展望未来了\Nbut I think it's time for us to focus on our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,大个儿吉姆那个混蛋呢\NWhere's that piece of crap-- Big Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.56,0:08:23.96,Default,,0,0,0,,他和丽贝卡·佩恩将被提审\NHe and Rebecca Pine will be arraigned
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.10,0:08:25.62,Default,,0,0,0,,并在陪审团面前审判\Nand tried in front of a jury.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,过程公平公正\NThe process will be fair and impartial.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.29,0:08:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,首先我想谈谈食物情况\NFirst, though, I'd like to talk to you about the food situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.52,0:08:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,储粮不足了\NSupplies are running low.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,但是不必恐慌\NBut there's no need to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.35,0:08:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以一起克服难关\NWe can get through this by coming together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我将发起自愿捐献食物行动\NWhich is why I'm initiating a voluntary food share program.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.98,0:08:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,大家可以将自己的食物\NPeople can bring whatever they have
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.40,0:08:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,拿到切斯特磨坊镇消防站\Nto the Chester's Mill fire station.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,志愿者将监督分配\NVolunteers will oversee distribution,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.45,0:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,确保人人得食\Ninsuring no one goes hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我放弃家人的食物吗  这太疯狂了\NYou want me to give up my family's food? That's crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,参与完全自愿\NParticipation is completely voluntary.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,但是聚合资源\NBut pooling our resources
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.60,0:08:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,是保证每个人都吃上饭的最好方法\Nis the best way to insure everyone gets fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.73,0:09:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那个混蛋来了\NThere's the son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要杀我们  吉姆\NWhy'd you try to kill us all, Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的一切  都是为了小镇\NEverything I did, I did for this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我爱切斯特磨坊镇\NI love Chester's Mill,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.60,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我会证明自己的清白\Nand I'll prove that I'm innocent of these charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.50,0:09:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你好运  亲爱的\NGood luck, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,今天  我们在此审讯吉姆·雷尼和丽贝卡·佩恩\NToday, we arraign Jim Rennie and Rebecca Pine
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.02,0:09:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-主要罪名有以下几项  -都是谎言\N- on the following charges. - It's all lies!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你才该接受审讯  不是他\NYou deserve to be on trial, not him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-对  -对\N- Yeah! - Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.21,0:09:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,-等一下  -吉姆  告诉我们你干了什么\N- Wait a minute. - Jim, Tell us what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,大家先冷静  听她说完\NFolks, calm down and let her speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大家冷静  退后  先让她说\NCalm down! Back up. Let her speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.19,0:09:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔  你得先把他们带走\NPhil, you got to get them out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.35,0:09:42.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大个儿吉姆  丽贝卡  我们走\NBig Jim, Rebecca, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,有枪\NGun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了\NHe's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.43,0:10:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}穹顶之下  第二季第五集
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.06,0:10:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我不敢相信波琳竟然还活着\NI just can't believe Pauline's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.40,0:10:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么她要让我们以为她去世这么久了\NWhy would she let us believe that she was dead for so long,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.65,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-即使她是想保护我们  -你当时还小\N- even if she was protecting us? - You were a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.61,0:10:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,可能你需要保护  但我不需要\NMaybe you needed protecting. I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,波琳开始说什么穹顶的事时\NWhen Pauline started ranting about some dome,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不相信她了\NI stopped believing in her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这让她崩溃了\NIt crushed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但到底是什么人\NBut what kind of person
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,才会让自己的哥哥和儿子为她哀痛了十年\Nlets her brother and her son spend a decade mourning,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,而自己却在那儿给疯子前男友寄明信片\Nwhile she sends postcards to her insane ex-boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还不提醒我们真正要死去的人是谁\NAnd not warning us about the people who were really gonna die,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.06,0:11:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,比如安琪\Nlike Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.37,0:11:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我能联系上她\NIf I could just get to her,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,事情肯定不会到这个地步\Nthings would be different.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,她肯定会告诉我所做之事是否正确\NShe'd tell me if I was doing the right thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我失去妈妈时\NWhen I lost Mom,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.36,0:11:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉那是最痛苦的事了\Nit was the worst pain ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,直到后来又失去了安琪\NUntil Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,莱尔夺走了我最美好的东西\NLyle took the best thing I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,要是让我找到他  我一定让他受苦\NAnd when I find him, I'm gonna make him suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.39,0:11:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,然后再一枪解决了他\NRight before I put a bullet between his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.34,0:11:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,知道吗  孩子\NYou know what, kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.36,0:11:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,可能不见的那几页日记\NMaybe those missing journal pages
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,就是找到莱尔的关键\Nare the key to finding Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我到处都找过了\NI've been looking for 'em everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我可能还知道一个地方\NI might know a place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.90,0:11:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,要怪也只能怪你自己\NYou only have yourself to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.94,0:11:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你和吉姆\NYou and Jim
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.38,0:11:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那个人口削减计划把大家都吓坏了\Nand your insane reduction plan has people terrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.50,0:11:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,所幸今天只有温德尔死了\NWe're lucky only Wendell died today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.21,0:11:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,否则他指不定打中谁呢\NAnybody could have been hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,可能是一个孩子  是我或者你\Na kid or me or you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.29,0:12:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.07,0:12:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,跟你说明一下\NJust so you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.78,0:12:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆说芭比也参与了\Nwhat Jim said about Barbie being involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,都是假的\Nhe wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.19,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们背着他行动的\NWe went behind his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,芭比一直相信还有其它办法\NBarbie always believed there was another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.00,0:12:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔  住手\NPhil, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.09,0:12:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么  你又管不着我\NWhy? I don't answer to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.55,0:12:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么管不着你  现在镇子由我负责\NYes, you do. This town put me in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.93,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,大个儿吉姆让我当警长\NWell, Big Jim made me sheriff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.19,0:12:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,大家有危险时  我就得有所行动\NAnd when people are at risk, I act.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.29,0:12:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你本来可以逮捕温德尔的\NYou could have just arrested Wendell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,芭比已经夺下他的枪了  可你却杀了他\NBarbie had already disarmed him. Instead you killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.82,0:12:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的一切都是为了保护这个小镇\NI did what I had to do to keep this town safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.36,0:12:44.25,Default,,0,0,0,,温德尔死了  更不用说莱尔是在你的看管下\NWendell is dead. Not to mention the fact that Lyle escaped
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.25,0:12:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,逃跑了  而且现在还不知所踪\Non your watch and is still on the loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,或许你肩负不起警长这个责任\NMaybe that badge is too big for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.36,0:12:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你想让我辞职吗\NYou want me to quit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-你要逼我吗  -不  不是她\N- You gonna make me? - No, not her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.73,0:12:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,是我\NMe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.46,0:13:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个\NYou two...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.08,0:13:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,真的沉迷于权力了啊\Nreally are drunk on power, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.84,0:13:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等着看大个儿吉姆怎么说吧\NWe'll see what Big Jim has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,如果现在做警长的是你而不是菲尔\NIf you'd been sheriff today instead of Phil,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.78,0:13:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-就不会有人死了  -茱莉亚\N- no one would've been killed. - Julia...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你的背景很合适\NYou have the perfect background.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-你接受过军事训练  -几小时前\N- Your military training... - A-And a few hours ago
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你还指责我跟大个儿吉姆站在一边\Nyou accused me of siding with Big Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.23,0:13:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你又让我\NNow you want me to be the person in charge
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,负责看管他\Nof keeping him locked up?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我该相信你的\NI should have trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.59,0:13:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉我怀疑你了\NI'm sorry I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.48,0:13:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,听你这么说真好\NThat's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.35,0:13:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,这个镇子会让人与人之间莫名其妙就反目成仇\NThis town just has a funny way of turning on people,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想这么快就再搅入战局\Nand I'm not ready to jump back into the fray.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂\NI get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找别人\NI'll find someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了\NI'm gonna go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:13:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,莱尔还在逍遥法外\NLyle's still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,可能他跟山姆在一起\NMaybe he's with Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会找到他们  然后让他们同处一室\NYeah, well, we'll find 'em, we'll put 'em in a room together
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,弄明白多年前到底发生了什么\Nand find out what the hell happened all those years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.29,0:14:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,必须如此\NWe have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,为了梅兰妮\NFor Melanie's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.77,0:14:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.17,0:14:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你碰穹顶时  它会显示什么吗\NSo when you touch the dome, it shows you stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,对\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,会显示幻象之类的东西\NLike, visions, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗\NSeriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.45,0:14:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你告诉我们你死了  我们都信你了\NHey, you told us you died and we got on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,有点团队精神好嘛\NHave some team spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.66,0:14:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,那要是它让我看到了一些不好的事呢\NBut what if it shows me something awful?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你会克服的  我们都习惯了\NYou'll get over it. We have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.40,0:14:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次碰穹顶的时候\NWhen you touch the dome for the first time,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,会有点触电的感觉\Nit's gonna give you a little shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你害怕了\NSo if you get scared,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.54,0:14:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,那就放手\Njust let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.68,0:15:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,看到什么了吗\NWhat do you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.13,0:15:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,什么都没有\NNothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,什么也没有\NAbsolutely nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定吗\NYou sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.55,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经很仔细地搜过这里了\NI already searched this place pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.34,0:15:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识莱尔很久了\NI've known Lyle a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这家伙鬼把戏太多了\NGuy's got a lot of tricks up his sleeve.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你看吧\NWell, what do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.99,0:15:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到了\NYou found 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.34,0:15:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看见了吗\NSee?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈的确画过安琪\NYour mom did draw Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.48,0:15:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,莱尔偷走这些是不想让我知道他干了什么\NLyle stole these to keep me from knowing what he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:46.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但为什么要杀安琪\NBut-but why kill Angie?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,他几乎都不认识她\NHe hardly knew her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.82,0:15:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,或许跟这个有关系\NMaybe this has something to do with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,四只手\NThe four hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.08,0:15:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,波琳絮絮叨叨说过很多事\NPauline ranted about a lot of things:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,粉色星星  困住我们的穹顶\Npink stars, a dome that would trap us
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.53,0:16:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,还有会保护穹顶的四只手\Nand the four hands that would be its protectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.36,0:16:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,她以前经常说  四只手会撑起穹顶\NShe used to say, four hands will hold up the dome,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.55,0:16:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,没有它们  穹顶会落下\Nand without them, it will fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.12,0:16:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是如果少了一只手  穹顶就会落下\NLike if one of the hands wasn't around, the dome would come down?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,所以莱尔才那么做\NThat's why Lyle did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.32,0:16:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他杀了安琪是为了让穹顶落下\NHe killed Angie to bring down the dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.87,0:16:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,这么说安琪是四只手之一\NSo Angie was one of the four hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,可能需要四个人都死才能有用\NMaybe all four hands have to die for it to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我得走了\NI have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.51,0:16:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我得确定其它手没事\NI have to make sure the other hands are okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.21,0:16:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,其它手\NThe other hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.85,0:16:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道他们是谁吗\NDo you know who they are?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.13,0:16:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.88,0:16:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,乔  诺莉和我\NJoe, Norrie and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.23,0:16:35.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果莱尔认为杀了我们四个人\NIf Lyle thinks that killing the four hands
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.83,0:16:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就能让穹顶落下\Nwill bring down the dome,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们任何一个都可能是下一个目标\Nany one of us could be next.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.51,0:16:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,吉姆\NHey, Jim?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.57,0:16:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你见过人死吗\NYou ever seen a man die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.35,0:16:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我是说\NI mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.08,0:16:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,今天以前\Nbefore today?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,很不幸  我见过\NIt's a sad fact of my life that I have, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那\NSo...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.12,0:17:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你是\Nhow do you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么面对的\Ndeal with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我想这是大局的一部分\NJust by knowing it's all part of a larger design.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.75,0:17:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,温德尔的死让我们都活了下来\NWendell's death means we get to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.31,0:17:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我很确定这交易挺划算的\NI'm sure that's a pretty good trade-off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我之前对我们的人口计划也是这么想的\NThat-that's what I told myself about our population plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.01,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是今天\NBut today...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.15,0:17:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,眼睁睁看着温德尔死去\Nwatching the life go out of Wendell...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.54,0:17:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,死亡并不美丽  丽贝卡\NDeath isn't pretty, Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但有时是必须的\NSometimes it's necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.99,0:17:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我总是很公正地看事情\NI've always looked at things clinically.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,做测试  得出结果  然后采取行动\NRun tests, you get results and then take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得这让我很强大\NI thought it made me strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.00,0:17:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是\NBut?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我昨天在教堂\NWhen I was in the church yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.70,0:17:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,准备要释放病毒的时候  看到那些人\Nabout to release the virus, and I saw those families,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.98,0:17:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,让我想起了我的妈妈\Nit reminded me of my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.87,0:18:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当我想起这样会造成很多家庭痛苦\NAnd when I thought about causing all those families to suffer
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.99,0:18:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,就像她当时那样  我...\Nthe way she did, I..
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是你没有释放病毒的原因\NThat's why you couldn't do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.38,0:18:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我爸爸是对的呢\NWhat if my dad was right
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.50,0:18:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,有时候一些问题真的没有答案\Nand sometimes there really aren't answers?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.89,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,可能你爸爸是对的\NWell, maybe your dad is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.95,0:18:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,但我们不能停止尝试\NThat doesn't mean we stop trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你\NLook, I trusted you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.10,0:18:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我支持你\NI had your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我也需要你支持我\NI need you to have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.88,0:18:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你说得对\NYou're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.50,0:18:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我支持你\NI-I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}禁止随地吐痰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,大个儿吉姆\NBig Jim!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.53,0:18:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,上班时喝酒啊  警长\NDrinking on the job, Sheriff?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,非也\NNope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,因为茱莉亚把我开除了\N'Cause Julia fired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.59,0:18:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我得偷偷躲过我的警官们才能到这\NI had to sneak past my own deputies to get in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.21,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧\NOh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这样做可不对\Nthat ain't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你是个好人  菲尔\NYou're a good man, Phil.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,这个小镇最好的警长\NThe best Sheriff this town's ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.49,0:19:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,比杜克还好\NBetter than Duke?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,还有琳达\NAnd Linda.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算释放病毒\NYour plan to release that virus...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.30,0:19:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你没有别的选择了  对吧\Nyou had no other choice, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,病毒不在我这里\NI didn't even have the virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.98,0:19:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,在丽贝卡那里\NRebecca did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果我们什么都不做\NBut if we don't do something,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.37,0:19:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们谁都不能活着出去了\Nthen none of us are gonna get out of here alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在茱莉亚让你做了她的替罪羊\NAnd now Julia's made you her scapegoat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.80,0:19:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,恰恰在这个小镇最需要你的时候\NRight when this town need you most.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  等等  不  不行  不能这样\NWait, wait, wait. No, no, no. Not that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.47,0:19:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,小镇一半的人都恨我  好吧\NHalf this town hates me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.73,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你放了我  他们会\NIf you let me out, they're gonna...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,他们会把我绑起来\Nthey're gonna string me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.32,0:19:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们该怎么挽回\NThen how do we make this right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.10,0:20:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得赢得他们的心\NWe got to win over their hearts and minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.97,0:20:08.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还是什么都没有\NStill nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.99,0:20:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,穹顶好像也有自己的想法\NThe dome kind of has a mind of its own.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.57,0:20:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,可能它现在心情不好\NMaybe it's not in the mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.67,0:20:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我们同时碰它怎么样\NWhat if we try touching it at the same time?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.01,0:20:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我和诺莉碰的时候都有反应\NWorked for me and Norrie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.08,0:20:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们不是不死怪物\NBecause you guys aren't some kind of undead freak.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.58,0:20:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮  我们会想出办法的\NMelanie, we're gonna figure this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,需要多长时间\NHow long will that take?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.06,0:20:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我还是不明白我为什么会复活\NI still have no idea why I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.07,0:20:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都不知道为什么被困在这个大鱼缸里\NNone of us know why we're trapped inside this fishbowl.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你得面对\NYou need to deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.34,0:20:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这么去想  以前你活着  然后死了\NThink of it this way: you were alive, then dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,现在又活了\Nnow alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,活两次死一次挺好的\NTwo out of three ain't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.48,0:20:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你不明白我经历的是什么\NYou don't know what I'm going through.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.65,0:20:37.78,Default,,0,0,0,,对  我不知道\NNo, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但我知道如果能让我妈妈复活\NBut I know how much I'd give
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我愿意付出多少\Nto have my mom alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我会马上用你\NIf it'd bring her back,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,长眠于这个陨石坑来做交换\NI'd trade you rotting in the bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要这样能带她回来\Nof that crater in a heartbeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道  我一直为你说话\NYou know, I've defended you a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.41,0:20:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,但有时你真的很让人讨厌\Nbut sometimes you're a real bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.54,0:21:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮  等等\NMelanie, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.51,0:21:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,乔\NJoe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.59,0:21:10.89,Default,,0,0,0,,诺莉  你们在家吗\NNorrie?! Are you guys here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也不在这\NThey aren't here either.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.84,0:21:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们该去茱莉亚家\NMaybe we should head back to Julia's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.35,0:21:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也不在那\NThey weren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.36,0:21:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,也不在野蔷薇或是镇上其它地方\NOr at the Sweetbriar or anywhere else in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会莱尔已经抓住他们了\NWhat if Lyle already got 'em?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.58,0:21:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,如果他伤害了他们\NIf he hurts them,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.23,0:21:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我永远都不会原谅我自己\NI won't be able to forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.58,0:21:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,小詹姆斯  如我之前所说\NJunior, like I said before,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,莱尔绝不可能知道他们是四只手\Nthere's no way Lyle could know they're part of the four hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你的朋友很安全\NYour friends are safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.21,0:21:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你在找什么\NWhat are you looking for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.01,0:21:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你得休息下平复下心情\NYou got to take a minute and calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.12,0:21:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样对谁都没好处\NYou're no good to anyone in this state.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,在穹顶降下后你就没喝过酒\NYou haven't had a drink since the dome came down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.40,0:21:45.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定要这么做\NYou sure you want to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.67,0:21:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我死去的妹妹其实还活着\NMy dead sister's alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.51,0:21:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我的外甥被一个疯子盯上了\Nmy nephew's on some nutball's hit list.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.92,0:21:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我想要这么做\NYeah, I want to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.91,0:22:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,再来一杯\NAnother one?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.26,0:22:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮\NMelanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.36,0:22:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,梅兰妮\NMelanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.16,0:22:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你得理解\NYou got to understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.75,0:22:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-关于诺莉  -不关她的事\N- about Norrie... - It's not her,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.40,0:22:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,是我自己\Nit's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.41,0:22:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要开心  但是\NI want to be happy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.98,0:22:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我感觉好孤单\NI feel so alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.43,0:22:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我的存在也不正常\NAnd I'm not normal, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.35,0:22:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,对我你是真实存在的\NYou're real to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.94,0:23:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,碰了穹顶没找到你的答案\NDidn't find your answers touching the Dome, hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.82,0:23:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,把舌头伸进他嘴里你也许就能找到答案了\Nmaybe you'll find 'em by sticking your tongue down his throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.28,0:23:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,实际上我一直奇怪他看上了你什么\NActually, what I'm wondering is what he sees in you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.46,0:23:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你对他和其它所有人的态度都很差\Nsince you treat him and everyone else like crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.32,0:23:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\NHey, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.30,0:23:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,诺莉  你没事吧\NNorrie, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.45,0:23:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,别假惺惺  乔\NDon't even, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.78,0:23:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你流血了\NYou're bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快也会流的\NAnd you're about to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个主意\NI've got an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.77,0:23:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}自愿捐献食物行动
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.65,0:23:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,给你\NHere we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.32,0:23:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,食物捐献行动还顺利吗\NFood drive's doing well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.49,0:23:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  结果挺不错的\NYeah, I mean, it's a decent turnout,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.34,0:23:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但要想最终成功\Nbut for this to work...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.09,0:23:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我们需要每个人的捐助\N...we need everyone's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.51,0:23:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把这些放到冰箱里\NI'm gonna put these in the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你能把那些箱子堆起来吗\NOh, can you stack those boxes?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.31,0:23:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好的\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.89,0:24:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,卡罗琳\NCarolyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.73,0:24:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.99,0:24:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚在哪\NWhere's Julia?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.24,0:24:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,还在里面\NStill inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.57,0:24:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚\NJulia!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.30,0:24:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我在这里\NOver here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.54,0:25:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好了  过来\NAll right. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.05,0:25:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,过来  这边\NCome on. This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.95,0:25:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,快走\NGo!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.18,0:25:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}自愿捐献食物行动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.07,0:25:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}自愿捐献食物行动
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.41,0:25:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能安全进入楼内\NAs soon as it's safe to enter the building,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.96,0:25:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会马上评估损失  看还剩余多少\Nwe will assess the damage, see what remains.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.53,0:25:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我剩下的所有食物都在里面\NThe last of my food was in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.99,0:25:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,今晚我的家人该吃什么\NWhat's my family supposed to eat tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.56,0:25:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了  我只需要大家保持冷静\NPlease, I just need everyone to stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.79,0:25:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别告诉我们保持冷静\NDon't tell us to stay calm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.37,0:25:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔  注意你的言行\NHey, Phil, watch yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.30,0:26:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我现在都不能说话了吗\NSo I can't even speak now?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.66,0:26:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,这些人需要知道真相\NThese people need to know the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.61,0:26:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚的绝妙计划\NJulia's big plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.45,0:26:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,不过是为了拿走大家的食物\Nwas just a way to take everybody's food away from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.17,0:26:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么都没拿走\NI didn't take anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.09,0:26:09.49,Default,,0,0,0,,然后她把所有食物都存放在一起\NThen she sticks it all in one place,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.49,0:26:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,旁边还有个很久又年久失修的发动机\Nalong with an old, beat-up generator.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.78,0:26:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果她能事先检查下\NNow, if she had bothered to check,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.07,0:26:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,就会发现那电线已经磨损了\Nshe would have seen that the wires were frayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.29,0:26:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大个儿吉姆就不会犯这种错误\NBig Jim never would have made that mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.35,0:26:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,而现在我们都会挨饿了\NAnd now we're all gonna starve.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.16,0:26:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我要拿什么喂我的孩子们\NWhat am I gonna feed my kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.40,0:26:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-明天我的食物从哪来  -好了\N- Where am I gonna get food tomorrow? - All-All right,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.07,0:26:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证我会查明到底发生了什么\NI promise I will get to the bottom of what happened
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.64,0:26:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,并找出解决方案\Nand find a solution.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.20,0:26:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是需要大家冷静一点\NI just need everyone to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.17,0:26:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这事还没完\NThis is not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.72,0:27:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NYou okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.01,0:27:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们搞砸了\NWe're screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.98,0:27:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,而且菲尔说得没错  这都是我的错\NAnd Phil's right, it's all my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.20,0:27:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我没检查发电机\NI didn't check the generators,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.11,0:27:09.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我根本没想到要检查\NI didn't even think to check.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.91,0:27:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,我和你的关系也搞砸了\NAnd I screwed up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.24,0:27:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该相信你的\NI should have believed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.09,0:27:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你也可以这样说我  听到了吗\NThat goes both ways. Do you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.25,0:27:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都犯了错\NWe both made mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.78,0:27:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,现在怎么办\NWhat now?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.64,0:27:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们去查出是谁引起的爆炸\NNow we figure out who caused the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.67,0:27:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔说是因为电线磨损\NPhil said the wires were frayed.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.64,0:27:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不相信他吗\NYou don't believe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.58,0:27:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不相信  肯定有隐情\NNo, there's something else going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.68,0:27:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就在爆炸前我发现了很多空箱子\NI found a bunch of empty boxes right before that explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.01,0:27:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这镇上只有一个人能做到\NThere's only one person in town who could do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.98,0:27:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我想问那个人是谁\NWell, I'd ask who that was,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.17,0:27:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但答案显而易见\Nbut it's a little obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.74,0:27:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我去跟大个儿吉姆谈谈\NI'll go talk with Big Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.73,0:27:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望我知道该怎么做\NI just wish I knew what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.99,0:27:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不管怎么做  我好像都没法\NYou know, no matter what, I can't seem
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.20,0:27:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,让镇上大部分居民满意\Nto please more than half the town at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.25,0:28:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,别放弃\NDon't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.48,0:28:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,有办法的  你会找到的\NThere's a way out of this. You're gonna find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.16,0:28:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,好吗\NOkay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.60,0:28:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NYou okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.24,0:28:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉\NSorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.48,0:28:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,不  请让我来\NNo, please, let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.22,0:28:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这会显示什么\NSo what's this gonna show?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.24,0:28:48.44,Default,,0,0,0,,希望会有我们之间的不同\NHopefully if there are differences between us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.94,0:28:51.33,Default,,0,0,0,,像我这样一直活着的人\NA guy who's always been alive, me,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.33,0:28:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,和\Nand...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.23,0:28:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你这样的人\Nsomeone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.45,0:28:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不同吗\NAre we different?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.41,0:28:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不确定\NUh, not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.14,0:29:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,有点超出了我能理解的范围\NLittle out of my depth here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.94,0:29:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,佩恩女士绝对能告诉我们这是什么意思\NMs. Pine would definitely be able to tell us what this means.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.45,0:29:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们怎么做  帮她越狱吗\NSo, what, we break her out of jail?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.29,0:29:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是随口一说\NI'm just saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.00,0:29:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,她想杀掉镇上所有的人\NShe tried to kill everyone in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.18,0:29:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须做点什么\NWe can't just do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.40,0:29:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这血液可能说明了我的身份\NThis blood thing could be the answer to who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.05,0:29:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  或者跟别的事一样\NYeah, or end up like everything else--
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.08,0:29:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,毫无结果\Nbig, fat, dead end.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.18,0:29:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哎哟\NWell, well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.19,0:29:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧这是谁  你现在是警长了\NLook who it is. You sheriff by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.64,0:29:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,还是新蜂王任命你为\NOr did new Queen Bee just go ahead and anoint you
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.11,0:29:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,切斯特磨坊镇的国王了\Nking of Chester's Mill?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.18,0:29:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴  吉姆\NOh, shut your mouth, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.32,0:29:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这下面可没有观众\NThere's no audience down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.45,0:29:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,消防站爆炸了\NThere was an explosion at the firehouse.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.58,0:29:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,所有储存在那里的食物都被炸毁了\NAll the food that was stored there's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.57,0:29:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得我会烧毁食物\NYou think I'd put this town at risk
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.44,0:29:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,来让这座小镇处于危险之中吗\Nby burning up its food supply?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.55,0:29:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是疯狂的新地步  芭比  就算对你而言\NThat's a new level of crazy, Barbie, even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.25,0:29:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.46,0:29:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔\NPhil.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.69,0:30:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,他之前来这里抱怨\NHe was down here grousing about
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.55,0:30:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚拿走了他的警徽  然后他提到了\NJulia taking his badge and he mentioned something
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.98,0:30:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,食物计划的事\Nabout the food program.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.44,0:30:05.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算这样玩啊\NSo that's how you're gonna play this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.87,0:30:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你打算让菲尔背黑锅\NYou're gonna throw Phil under the bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.77,0:30:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,别听我的  去问丽贝卡吧\NWell, don't take my word for it, ask... ask Rebecca.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.24,0:30:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔进来时我一定睡着了\NI must have been asleep when Phil came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.40,0:30:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我什么也没听见\NI didn't hear anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.62,0:30:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,想得美  吉姆\NNice try, Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.25,0:30:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧  你接下来要一直以为\NFine. You're gonna go about your day
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.78,0:30:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,爆炸是我搞的鬼\Nthinking I'm responsible for the explosion,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.65,0:30:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,那真是...\Nthat's, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.94,0:30:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,做好准备迎接\NJust be ready for whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.35,0:30:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔接下来计划的疯狂事吧\Nmadness Phil has planned next.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.26,0:31:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,菲尔\NPhil?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.79,0:31:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你在这里干什么\NWhat are you doing in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.16,0:31:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,确保这地方的安全\NJust making sure the place is secure.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.29,0:31:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这里面有食物吗\NIs there food in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.00,0:31:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没用这间房\NWe weren't using this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.61,0:31:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,也许有人搬了食物\NMaybe someone moved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.35,0:31:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么\NWhy would they?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.39,0:31:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,除非他们知道会有爆炸\NUnless they knew the explosion was coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.76,0:32:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈对所有人都撒谎了\NMy mom lied to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.16,0:32:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,她唯一爱的人是莱尔\NThe only one she loves is Lyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.22,0:32:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我听到了  哥们\NI hear you, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.56,0:32:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们都疯了\NAnd they're both crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.85,0:32:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,他们一起是疯上加疯\NThey're crazying it up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.33,0:32:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你得好好睡一觉\NYou got to sleep this one off.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.03,0:32:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我不想这样对你\NI don't want to do this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.07,0:32:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你或者安琪\NYou or Angie.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.25,0:32:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,如果还有其它方法\NIf there was any other way
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.09,0:32:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来摧毁穹顶  我会做的\Nto bring the Dome down, I'd do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.92,0:32:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.56,0:33:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你照顾我\NThanks for looking out for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.34,0:33:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我只剩你这个家人了\NYou're the only family I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.69,0:33:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,爱你  山姆舅舅\NLove you, Uncle Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.33,0:33:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,趴下\NHey, on the ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.35,0:33:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,马上趴下\NGet on the ground right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.22,0:33:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不  芭比  你要这么做\NNo, Barbie, that's what you're going to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.11,0:33:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,别这样  你不是这种人  菲尔\NOh, come on, this is not you, Phil.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.39,0:33:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你不想伤害任何人\NI know you don't want to hurt anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.68,0:34:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,放了她  菲尔\NDrop her, Phil.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.72,0:34:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能再做英雄了  芭比\NYou're done being the hero, Barbie.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.27,0:34:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,快放了她\NDrop... now!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.96,0:34:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吧\NYou all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.39,0:34:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.89,0:34:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,你呢\NYou?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.63,0:34:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,现在没事了\NI am now.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.82,0:34:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚\NJulia.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.09,0:34:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真是惊喜\NWhat a nice surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.43,0:34:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你有空吗\NDo you have a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.52,0:34:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是在想野蔷薇餐馆发生的事\NI'm just wondering about what's happening at the Sweetbriar Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.55,0:35:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我看见你在那里给大家分发食物\NI see you there, feeding everyone, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.62,0:35:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我想知道食物是从哪里来的\NI wonder where the food is coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.61,0:35:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,地下储藏室\NThe basement pantry.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.91,0:35:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我刚看过那儿了  里面是空的\NI just checked there-- it's empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.15,0:35:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,安德莉亚  你做得很好\NAndrea, you're doing an amazing job.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.29,0:35:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小镇居民活下来全是因为你\NThe town continues to live because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.82,0:35:18.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我该代表大伙儿问一问\NI just think I owe it to everyone to at least ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.43,0:35:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我得带你去看一样东西\NThere's something I have to show you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.15,0:35:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.86,0:35:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是开始\NThis is just the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.31,0:35:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,整个地下储藏室都满了\NThe entire basement is filled.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.14,0:35:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,食物足以供给全镇居民吃几个月\NThere's enough to feed the whole town for a couple of months.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.46,0:35:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪里弄来这么多食物\NWhere did you get all this food?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.96,0:35:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我去世的丈夫洛伊德的\NFrom Lloyd, my late husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.04,0:35:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,洛伊德称自己为活命主义者\NLloyd called himself a survivalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.07,0:35:52.13,Default,,0,0,0,,他总是能预见即将发生的糟糕事\NHe always saw something bad around the corner.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.49,0:35:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,谢天谢地\NThank God.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.90,0:35:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他说危机来临时\NSaid when the crisis hit,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.28,0:35:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都会只为自己\Nit'd be every man for himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.39,0:36:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我没有主动站出来\NI'm sorry I didn't come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.76,0:36:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是害怕有人会偷走食物\NI was just scared someone would steal it from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.24,0:36:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但我信任你\NBut I trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.42,0:36:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你该使用\NYou should use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.08,0:36:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一起用\NWe'll use it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.98,0:36:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,山姆舅舅\NUncle Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.84,0:36:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我上二年级时  我妈妈画了那幅画\NMy mom painted that when I was in the second grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.71,0:36:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我拿这幅画进行展示和讲述\NI brought it in for show-and-tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.13,0:36:47.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我猜你从来没看过这个吧\NI'm guessing you've never seen this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.52,0:36:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\NOh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.29,0:36:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,方尖塔\NThe obelisk.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.57,0:37:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我有次做梦梦见过\NI saw this in a dream I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.90,0:37:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈妈也在场\NMy mom was there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.30,0:37:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,1821\N1821.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.94,0:37:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,那是安琪被杀之处的\NThat's the number of the locker at school
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.35,0:37:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,学校储物柜编号\Nwhere Angie got killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.32,0:37:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你妈妈日记的最后一页也写了\NIt's also in your mother's journal, on the last page.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.08,0:37:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我完全不知道这是什么意思\NI had no idea what it meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.95,0:37:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,莱尔逃跑前在日记里看到了什么\NLyle saw something in the journal before he ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.25,0:37:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,也许他又去储物柜那边了\NMaybe he went back to the locker.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.23,0:37:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他为什么会去那里\NWhy would he go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.31,0:37:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  但这显然对他来说有意义\NI don't know, but it obviously means something to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.14,0:37:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,也许我们没找到莱尔  是因为我们还没去查看那里\NMaybe we haven't found Lyle 'cause we haven't checked there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.16,0:37:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这太棒了\NThis is amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.69,0:37:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,简直就像七月的感恩节\NIt's like Thanksgiving in July.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.80,0:37:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,全靠茱莉亚\NIt's all Julia.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.39,0:37:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你从哪里弄来的食物\NWhere'd you get the food?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.07,0:37:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,行业秘密\NTrade secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.34,0:37:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,但一定要记得感谢安德莉亚\NBut make sure to thank Andrea
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.69,0:37:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,举办了这么一场盛会\Nfor hosting such a lovely event.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.63,0:37:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,一顿好吃的不能证明什么\NOne nice meal doesn't prove anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.75,0:37:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是大个儿吉姆\NYou're no Big Jim.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.88,0:37:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我让他来决定吧\NWell... I'll let him decide that.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.98,0:38:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在这里干什么呢\NWhat the hell are we doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.60,0:38:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,等着瞧吧\NOh, just wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.50,0:38:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,各位  我今早说了\NFolks, I, uh, said this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.23,0:38:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得我们镇民们\Nthat I thought it was time for us Millers
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.98,0:38:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,该着眼未来了\Nto focus on our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.24,0:38:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,但我觉得只有放下过去才能做到那点\NBut I don't think we can do that until we let go of the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.87,0:38:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是那些做过错事的人的行为\NEven the actions of those who have wronged us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.03,0:38:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,大个儿吉姆和丽贝卡昨天想做的事\NWhat Big Jim and Rebecca tried to do yesterday
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.61,0:38:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没有借口\Nis inexcusable...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.74,0:38:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,但并非不可原谅\N...but it's not unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.39,0:38:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以继续保持愤怒\NNow, we can stay angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.29,0:38:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,跟对方战斗到底  或者\Ntear each other apart, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.90,0:38:41.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以超越\Nwe can rise above,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.95,0:38:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,然后合作\Nand-and work together,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.54,0:38:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,保证我们在穹顶之下生存下去\Nand ensure our survival under this dome.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.38,0:38:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我承认\NI admit...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.64,0:38:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我犯过一些错\NI've made some mistakes...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.61,0:39:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但那都是为了这座小镇\Nbut all of them in service of this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.45,0:39:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的感谢茱莉亚\NAnd I really appreciate Julia
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.79,0:39:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,给我机会来\Ngiving me the chance to...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.21,0:39:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,赎罪\Nto make amends.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.96,0:39:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们都应该知道\NAnd you all should know...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.37,0:39:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我觉得她管理切斯特磨坊镇管理得很好\N...I think she's done a hell of a job running Chester's Mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:57.22,0:39:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好好享受吧  各位\NEnjoy yourself. Enjoy yourself, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.57,0:39:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,享受食物吧\NEnjoy the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.88,0:40:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我搞不懂你\NYou know, I don't understand you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.83,0:40:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直说你站在我这边\NYou keep saying you're on my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.93,0:40:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但你肯定对我心怀不满\Nbut it sure as hell seems like you've turned on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.92,0:40:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想着  也许\NI just think, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.30,0:40:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们该给茱莉亚一个机会\Nwe should give Julia a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.46,0:40:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,也许领导能仁慈点儿挺好的\NMaybe benevolence isn't such a bad quality in a leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:18.12,0:40:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,还是说仁慈会害死我们\NOr it's the thing that's gonna get us all killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.20,0:40:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧瞧你做的事\NLook what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.95,0:40:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,如果没有你的帮助  我做不成\NYeah, it wouldn't have happened without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.59,0:40:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我可说不好\NOh, I don't know about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.47,0:40:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你找到了你的警长吗\NHave you... you found your sheriff yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.90,0:40:31.35,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么  你有人选吗\NWhy, you have someone in mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.82,0:40:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧\NI might.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.12,0:40:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,之前的事我很抱歉\NI'm sorry about earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.56,0:40:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你吻了她  乔\NYou kissed her, Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.27,0:41:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  但是...\NYeah, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.73,0:41:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,她不是我爱的人\Nshe's not who I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.69,0:41:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你才是\NYou are.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.72,0:41:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你当着我的面\NThat's your go-to...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.22,0:41:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,和另一个妞儿乱搞  这就是你的借口吗\Nafter you've macked on another chick in front of my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.64,0:41:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在她身上试试吧\NTry it on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.16,0:41:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,她够蠢  会上当的\NShe's dumb enough to fall for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.79,0:41:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚  我很感受\NJulia... I'm impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.27,0:41:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,特别是你对吉姆和我做的事\NEspecially with what you did for Jim and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.48,0:41:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我做的是对小镇有益处的事\NI did what was best for the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.77,0:41:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是想道谢\NI just wanted to say thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.66,0:41:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,茱莉亚  我们有点问题\NJulia, we've got a quick question back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.62,0:41:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,乔说你真的很聪明\NJoe says you're really, really smart.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.20,0:41:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,像科学家一样\NLike a scientist.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.40,0:41:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\NThank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.37,0:41:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,我有个东西想让你搞明白\NI have something I want you to figure out.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.63,0:41:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,关于我的\NAbout me.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.53,0:42:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}梅兰妮
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.79,0:42:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}乔
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.51,0:42:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小詹姆斯  你在干嘛\NJunior? What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.68,0:42:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,安琪就是死在了这里\NThis is where Angie died.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.94,0:42:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,这里对凶手有意义\NIt meant something to the killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.47,0:42:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,看来这玩意儿被踢坏了\NLooks like the whole thing's been kicked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.65,0:42:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,把你的手电筒给我\NGive me your flashlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.54,0:42:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,这足够让一个男人进去\NIt's big enough for a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.46,0:42:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得莱尔就是消失在这里了吗\NDo you think this is where Lyle disappeared to?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.75,0:42:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这是个隧道\NIt's a tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.13,0:42:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  但是通向哪里呢\NYeah, but to where?
